text: Gunner Olesen (22 December 1916 - 24 February 1979) was a Danish gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1916 births Category:1979 deaths Category:Danish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Denmark Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:People from Slagelse
